## 1. Design Principles

### 1.1 Core Principles
- **Professional & Trustworthy** - B2B users expect enterprise-grade design
- **Efficient & Functional** - Streamlined workflows for business users
- **Consistent & Intuitive** - Familiar patterns and clear navigation
- **Responsive & Accessible** - Works across all devices and users

### 1.2 User Experience Goals
- **Reduce cognitive load** - Clear information hierarchy
- **Minimize clicks** - Efficient task completion
- **Provide feedback** - Clear status indicators and confirmations
- **Error prevention** - Proactive validation and helpful guidance

